caption.title: Electrochemical impedance spectra of Co 3O 4/TiO 2 hierarchical heterostructures.
caption.p: Nyquist plots before cycling for the pristine TiO 2 nanofibers, single Co 3O 4 nanostructures and Co 3O 4/TiO 2 hierarchical heterostructures by applying an AC voltage of 5 mV amplitude at 0.1 Hz to 700 kHz.
